4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring specialists with no prior experience. Over 16 weeks, participants receive foundational training in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, while acquiring practical skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The bootcamp features 3 live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. Courses are available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop